# After every action — verify

Before considering an edit complete, check:

- Does every new `pub struct` / `pub type` in a numeric crate carry
  `S: Strategy`? (`strategy-marker-required` lint)
- Does the crate compile with `cargo check` inside `mock/`?
- Does `cargo mock --lint-only` pass at `--commit` severity?
- Are new types named in the matching `DESIGN.md.tmpl`?
  (`undocumented-type` lint)
- Is there an open `*_changelist.src.md` in `design_rounds/` covering
  this source change? (`changelist-required` lint)
- Did you touch anything under `.claude/`, `.github/hooks/`,
  `.github/instructions/`, `.github/skills/`, or
  `.github/copilot-instructions.md`? Revert: edit `mock/agent/`
  templates instead, re-run `cargo mock`.
- Does the commit follow `type: lowercase imperative message` with
  no parentheses, no period, under 72 chars?
- Byline policy: non-autonomous mode rejects any `Co-Authored-By`
  unless `config.toml` configures a pattern. Autonomous mode
  requires one matching the configured pattern. Check
  `${ARVO_AGENT_MODE:-assistant}`.
